in exposing corruption.

101
00:05:19,987 --> 00:05:22,688
We helped bring down QuoVadis.

102
00:05:22,723 --> 00:05:24,505
We will be stronger together.

103
00:05:24,541 --> 00:05:26,140
Guaranteed.

104
00:05:28,195 --> 00:05:29,978
Well...

105
00:05:30,013 --> 00:05:33,464
