and get back to you.

106
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,784
In the meantime, Dr. Bell,

107
00:05:35,819 --> 00:05:39,053
do avoid any
further PR disasters.

108
00:05:42,942 --> 00:05:44,575
A bit of news for you.

109
00:05:44,611 --> 00:05:47,362
I'm putting a pacemaker
in Micah today.

110
00:05:47,397 --> 00:05:49,214
Alert the media.

111
00:05:49,249 --> 00:05:50,832
I know.

112
00:05:50,867 --> 00:05:52,684
It's minor.

113
00:05:52,719 --> 00:05:54,346
So, don't worry. You
don't need to be there.

114
00:05:54,370 --> 00:05:55,870
Why wouldn't I assist?

115
00:05:55,905 --> 00:05:57,901
