previous commitment.

141
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,421
- Oh?
- Double shift.

142
00:07:08,445 --> 00:07:10,440
This place is my main
squeeze these days.

143
00:07:10,464 --> 00:07:11,829
You're aware that's pathetic.

144
