178
00:08:34,113 --> 00:08:36,247
A new organ could
help her heart.

179
00:08:36,283 --> 00:08:40,434
Yeah. But we can't
wait years to get one.

180
00:08:43,456 --> 00:08:44,589
Excuse me.

181
00:08:44,624 --> 00:08:46,474
Hi. Welcome to Chastain.

182
00:08:46,509 --> 00:08:47,886
- Can I help you?
- Yeah, maybe.

183
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:49,310
I'm looking for a doctor.

184
00:08:49,345 --> 00:08:51,062
Her name is Shira Smook.

185
00:08:51,097 --> 00:08:54,265
Shira... Smook.

186
00:08:55,568 --> 00:08:57,435
Okay. Anesthesiology.

187
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:58,853
Would you like me to page her?

188
00:08:58,889 --> 00:09:01,355
Nah. Anesthesiology.

189
00:09:01,391 --> 00:09:02,574
I'll call her myself,

190
00:09:02,609 --> 00:09:04,041
