heart medication

197
00:09:24,665 --> 00:09:26,280
so you can tolerate dialysis.

198
00:09:32,673 --> 00:09:34,905
All right, Nic and I need
to discuss our options.

199
00:09:34,942 --> 00:09:36,240
Then I'll be right back.

200
00:09:38,278 --> 00:09:39,561
It's gonna be okay.

201
00:09:39,596 --> 00:09:41,313
Just give me a sec.

202
00:09:46,653 --> 00:09:48,052
Elevated JVP.

203
00:09:48,087 --> 00:09:50,939
And I saw signs of
hepatojugular reflux.

204
00:09:50,974 --> 00:09:53,591
