is getting worse,

205
00:09:53,627 --> 00:09:55,075
more rapidly than we expected.

206
00:09:55,111 --> 00:09:56,661
This is a disaster.

207
00:09:58,114 --> 00:10:01,282
Treatment of dual organ
failure is challenging,

208
00:10:01,335 --> 00:10:03,217
not impossible.

209
00:10:03,253 --> 00:10:05,953
Heart failure alone
could kill Jessie.

210
00:10:05,988 --> 00:10:07,955
She needs a new kidney.

211
00:10:07,991 --> 00:10:09,940
Soon.

212
00:10:09,977 --> 00:10:12,677
There are cases where that
alone improves heart function.

213
00:10:12,712 --> 00:10:15,613
